[center]I WANT COMMENT'S/IDEA'S FOR FUTURE UPDATES, COMMENT OR I WILL TAKE DOWN![/center]
[center][u][i]Project Unforgiven[/i][/u][/center]
Project Unforgiven Is my latest work. I was going to host It but then found out my Desktop wasn't going to be coming until next month. Tbh, I don't really wanna wait that long, So I'll release. I'm sorry It's a little sloppy. I haven't had that much time to clean It out..
[u][i]Server Features[/i][/u]
100% Combat 100% Prayer Working Report Abuse Working Ancient's, With Ancient's tab. (Thank you Sk1ttlez) Working Specials Working Wilderness Levels Working Summoning 138 Max Combat Fixed Max Cash (2147m)
blah blah.. all that good stuff.
[u][i] Special Features[/i][/u]
Dragon Claws Dragon Platebody Bandos full helm (custom model) Zaro's godsword with FULL Special
